data.description: Welcome home to your backyard aquatic oasis! Upon entering this meticulously maintained home, you'll notice the spacious and well thought out floor plan featuring three bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The living room and primary bedroom are both situated at the back of the home while both guest bedrooms are found up front. When you aren't hanging out downstairs, spend your summer nights out on the oversized screened in back porch. The back yard is an entertainer's dream boasting an in-ground spa, outdoor shower and lounging/game area. Don't miss your opportunity to own a slice of paradise on Oak Island! Owner is a licensed NC real estate broker.
